  "texts": [
    "Table 1 presents a series of prompt examples and the corresponding feedback generated by the GPT-4 turbo model in response to the student's statement \"The metal balls hit each other\".",
    "The prompts shown in this table correspond to the \"Instructions for the LLM\" part presented in Section III B.",
    "In addition to what is displayed in Table 1, we instruct the LLM on the student's visual context, for instance, \"The video presents a demonstration of Newton's cradle, or Newton's cradle, in motion\".",
    "Subsequently, we provide the special prompt type shown in the table and finally instruct the LLM, \"If the student's response contains information unrelated to the concepts presented in the video or if the student greets you, kindly request the student to focus on the video content\".",
    "This final instruction is designed to prevent the generation of responses when the student inputs something unrelated to the task."
